		"description": "<p>At 3rd level, your defensive abilities also improve with some help from your magical studies.</p>\n<p>If you have the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.mcvhe4g4bv9jt22k]{Brutal Defense} feature, you can spend 2 exertion points to infuse your armor with crackling magical energy for a minute. While this ability is active, a creature that hits you with a melee attack must make a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC. A creature that fails the save takes force damage equal to your martial arts die.</p>\n<p>If you have the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.zh0pv154q6abroh6]{Agile Defense} ability, you instead may instead use Flurry of Blows, Long Step, or Patient Defense after casting a spell with a casting time of one action.</p>",
